vote.title: Authorize the first of two, one-year renewal options to the service contract with Open Arms, Inc. dba Bryan’s House to provide single mothers with specialized childcare for their special needs children through the Overcoming Barriers to Work Program for the period of October 1, 2020 through September 30, 2021 - Not to exceed $36,698.00 from $36,698.00 to $73,396.00 - Financing:  2020-21 Community Development Block Grant Fund
